## Status legend

- ⬜ not started — no plan file yet
- 📝 planned — `docs/plans/story-N-*.md` exists, tests still `.skip`
- 🔨 coding — tests being written/passed
- 🧪 scoring — tests pass, awaiting `/eo-score`
- 🩹 bridging gaps — score 80–89, `/eo-bridge-gaps` running
- ✅ shipped — merged to main + deployed
- ⚠️ inconsistent — state checks failed, see `/eo-guide` diagnostic

## Invariants

- Score < 80 → status cannot be `shipped`
- `shipped` → must have both score ≥ 90 row AND deploy log entry
- `coding` without a plan file = impossible; `/eo-guide` flags as inconsistent

## MVP cadence (reference)

Sprint = 1 story → live URL. MVP = 4–7 sprints. Don't conflate them.

| Sprint | Weeks | Story target |
|--------|-------|--------------|
| 1 | Week 1 | Story 1 (+ Story 2 if simple) |
| 2 | Week 2 | Stories 3–4 |
| 3 | Week 3 | Stories 5–6 |
| 4 | Week 4 | Story 7 + full QA |
| 5 | Week 5 | Soft launch + 15 listings |
